The paper proposes a new method for generic segmentation using deep learning techniques. This topic falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of neural networks (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in the proposed method. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of graph representations (cs.GR) to improve the segmentation algorithm. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.LG, followed by cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.GR.
